#

Creamy Garlic Pasta

30 min
$12
750 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main

Tags:

PastaQuickComfort Food

Description

A rich and creamy pasta dish with a hint of garlic, perfect for a quick weeknight dinner.

Ingredients

  • pasta (spaghetti or fettuccine): 8 oz
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley: for garnish
